{"tid":2308550,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"未放低又點鐘意","createTime":"2020-12-02T03:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T03:29:17.000Z","uid":365331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"027573317767c2263e4d77d4c5ac15ec46987fd9","tid":2308550,"uid":365331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"一齊咗383日<br />\n<br />\n分咗手1039日<br />\n<br />\n一直都以為del哂關於你嘅所有野<br />\n<br />\n就可以令自己放得低<br />\n<br />\n明明都盡力忘記你<br />\n<br />\n點解呢幾日發夢又見返你<br />\n<br />\n點解一醒返眼角都有眼淚<br />\n<br />\n我知你同第二個拍緊2年拖<br />\n<br />\n我地都係一齊咗一年多少少姐<br />\n<br />\n你都跟咗第二個啦<br />\n<br />\n我都遇上咗其他好女仔啦<br />\n<br />\n點解我對佢地只有好感咋 未到鐘意呀<br />\n<br />\n點解我仲係未放得低你呀<br />\n<br />\n我想鐘意第二個姐<br />\n<br />\n好撚辛苦屌你老母"},{"pid":"ece7a65e1fefb1da16bb3980cecabec220a6acc7","tid":2308550,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2723022e85841a154fe41ad36047ec2826bf2f9a","tid":2308550,"uid":240396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}